title: Genesis - As Good As Gold: Live at Lyceum 1980 (m4a)
description:
Live recording of Genesis at the Lyceum Ballroom in London during their "Duke" tour in 1980:

DISC 1:
Deep In The Motherlode
Dancing With The Moonlit Knight (Intro)
The Carpet Crawlers
Squonk
One For The Vine
Behind The Lines
Duchess
Guide Vocal
Turn It On Again
Duke's Travels
Duke's End
Say It's Alright Joe

DISC 2:
The Lady Lies
Ripples
In The Cage/The Colony Of Slippermen
Afterglow
Follow You, Follow Me
Dance On A Volcao
Drum Duet
Los Endos
I Know What I Like (In Your Wardrobe)
The Knife

Enjoy!

Lineup:
Phil Collins - vocals, drums and percussion
Michael Rutherford - bass, guitars, bass pedals
Daryl Stuermer - bass, guitars
Tony Banks - keyboards
Chester Thompson - drums and percussion
